ResourceHeader.ResourceName: MMS2 Magnetic Ephemeris and Coordinates MEC MMS 2 Magnetic Ephemeris and Support (Tsyganenko 2004 Model, Disturbed Conditions), Quick-Look Survey
ResourceHeader.Description: MEC>Magnetic Ephemeris and Coordinates MMS MEC Magnetic ephemeris and coordinates, Level 2 science data. PI institution is Los Alamos National Laboratory (LANL)

Parameter.Name: Epoch
Parameter.Description: Nanoseconds from J2000 with leap seconds included.
Parameter.Caveats: This parameter exhibits an increasing monotonic progression.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_dipole_tilt
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Dipole tilt angle. Rotation angle (around Y-axis) between GSM and SM coordinate systems. In units of degrees.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_gmst
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Greenwich Mean Sidereal Time (GMST).

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_mlat
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Magnetic Latitude.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_mlt
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Magnetic Local Time.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_l_dipole
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Dipole L-shell value.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_quat_eci_to_bcs
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Quaternion rotation from GEI/J2000 to BCS (ECI to BCS). ((qx,qy,qz), qw)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_ang_mom_vec
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Right ascension (deg) and declination (deg) of angular momentum (L)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_ang_mom_phase
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: L-phase (Sun-to-body-X dihedral angle about angular momentum vector L) (deg)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_kp
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Kp index from QinDenton files (used as input to magnetic field models)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_dst
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Dst index from QinDenton files. Used as input to magnetic field models

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_earth_eclipse_flag
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Earth eclipse flag: 0 = no eclipse; 1 = penumbral eclipse; 2 = umbral eclipse.
Parameter.Caveats: This parameter exhibits an increasing monotonic progression.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_moon_eclipse_flag
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Moon eclipse flag: 0 = no eclipse; 1 = penumbral eclipse; 2 = umbral eclipse.
Parameter.Caveats: This parameter exhibits an increasing monotonic progression.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_r_eci
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geocentric Equatorial Inertial (GEI/J2000) position vector of mms2 (km)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_v_eci
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Velocity of mms2 spacecraft in GEI/J2000 (i.e. ECI) coordinates (km/s)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_r_gsm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geocentric Solar Magnetospheric (GSM) position vector of mms2 (km)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_v_gsm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Velocity of mms2 spacecraft in GSM coordinates (km/s)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_quat_eci_to_gsm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Quaternion rotation from GEI/J2000 to GSM (ECI to GSM). ((qx,qy,qz), qw)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_r_geo
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geocentric Geographic (GEO) position vector of mms2 (km)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_v_geo
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Velocity of mms2 spacecraft in GEO coordinates (km/s)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_quat_eci_to_geo
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Quaternion rotation from GEI/J2000 to GEO (ECI to GEO). ((qx,qy,qz), qw)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_r_sm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geocentric Solar Magnetic (SM) position vector of mms2 (km)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_v_sm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Velocity of mms2 spacecraft in SM coordinates (km/s)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_quat_eci_to_sm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Quaternion rotation from GEI/J2000 to SM (ECI to SM). ((qx,qy,qz), qw)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_r_gse
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geocentric Solar Ecliptic (GSE) position vector of mms2 (km)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_v_gse
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Velocity of mms2 spacecraft in GSE coordinates (km/s)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_quat_eci_to_gse
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Quaternion rotation from GEI/J2000 to GSE (ECI to GSE). ((qx,qy,qz), qw)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_r_gse2000
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geocentric Solar Ecliptic (J2000 Pole, GSE2000) position vector of mms2 (km)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_v_gse2000
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Velocity of mms2 spacecraft in GSE2000 coordinates (km/s)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_quat_eci_to_gse2000
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Quaternion rotation from GEI/J2000 to GSE2000 (ECI to GSE2000). ((qx,qy,qz), qw)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_geod_lat
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geodetic latitude of mms2 spacecraft

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_geod_lon
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geodetic longitude of mms2 spacecraft

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_geod_height
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geodetic height of mms2 spacecraft. (Height above WGS84 Spheroid.)

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_r_sun_de421_eci
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geocentric position vector (in km) of the Sun in GEI/J2000 Coordinates.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_r_moon_de421_eci
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geocentric position vector (in km) of the Moon in GEI/J2000 Coordinates.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_int_model
Parameter.Description: Internal Magnetic Field Model.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_ext_model
Parameter.Description: External Magnetic Field Model.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_fieldline_type
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Fieldline Type: 0 = IMF; 1 = Closed; 2 = Open Northern Lobe; 3 = Open Southern Lobe; -1 = Inside Earth; -2 = Target Height Unreachable; -3 = Bad Trace (error).
Parameter.Caveats: This parameter exhibits an increasing monotonic progression.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_bsc_gsm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Magnetic field (in GSM) at mms2 spacecraft

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_loss_cone_angle_s
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Southern loss cone angle. Degrees.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_loss_cone_angle_n
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Northern loss cone angle. Degrees.

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_pfs_geod_latlon
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geodetic latitude and longitude of southern footpoint (100km geodetic height) of field threading the mms2 spacecraft

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_pfn_geod_latlon
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Geodetic latitude and longitude of northern footpoint (100km geodetic height) of field threading the mms2 spacecraft

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_pfs_gsm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: GSM position southern footpoint (100km geodetic height) of field threading the mms2 spacecraft

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_bfs_gsm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Magnetic field (in GSM) at southern footpoint (100km geodetic height) of field threading the mms2 spacecraft

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_pfn_gsm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: GSM position northern footpoint (100km geodetic height) of field threading the mms2 spacecraft

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_bfn_gsm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Magnetic field (in GSM) at northern footpoint (100km geodetic height) of field threading the mms2 spacecraft

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_pmin_gsm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: GSM position of min-B point of field threading the mms2 spacecraft

Parameter.Name: mms2_mec_bmin_gsm
Parameter.Set: Time series defined by using: EPOCH
Parameter.Description: Magnetic field (in GSM) at min-B point of field threading the mms2 spacecraft
